开拓者119号，你可以起飞了。
Trailblazer 119, you are cleared for takeoff.

161
00:09:01,976 --> 00:09:04,544
保持跑道航向，上升2点，保持2000。
Maintain runway heading, climb two and maintain 2,000.

162
00:09:04,587 --> 00:09:06,546
收到，可以起飞了。
Roger that, and cleared for takeoff.

163
00:09:06,589 --> 00:09:07,677
飞跑道航向。
Fly runway heading.

164
00:09:07,721 --> 00:09:10,462
上升，保持2000。开拓者119。
Climb and maintain 2,000. Trailblazer 119.

165
00:09:10,506 --> 00:09:13,596
起飞功率已设置。空速活着。
Takeoff power is set. Airspeed alive.

166
00:09:15,076 --> 00:09:17,078
八十反复试验。
Eighty. Cross-checks.

167
00:09:18,383 --> 00:09:24,738
90 100 110 120 v - 1。
90, 100, 110, 120, V-one.

168
00:09:26,130 --> 00:09:27,262
旋转。
Rotate.

169
00:09:35,183 --> 00:09:37,925
-正确率，升起落架。-升起起落架。
- Positive rate, landing gear up. - Landing gear up.

170
00:09:37,968 --> 00:09:39,491
-折叠起来。-折叠起来。
- Flaps up. - Flaps up.

171
00:09:39,535 --> 00:09:43,321
开拓者119号，右转，航向106，零度。
Trailblazer 119, turn right, heading one-oh-six, zero degrees.

172
00:09:43,365 --> 00:09:45,367
1 - 2，保持1 - 0。
One-two and maintain one-zero thousand.

173
00:09:45,410 --> 00:09:47,064
离开副本。开拓者119。
Copy departure. Trailblazer 119.

174
00:09:51,982 --> 00:09:54,942
女士们先生们，我是机长。
Ladies and gentlemen, this is your captain speaking.

175
00:09:54,985 --> 00:09:57,640
我们已经达到了37000英尺的巡航高度。
We've reached our cruising altitude of 37,000 feet.

176
00:09:57,684 --> 00:10:00,184
如果你有什么需要…先生，要来点杏仁吗?
If there's anything you need... Sir, would you care for some almonds?

177
00:10:00,208 --> 00:10:01,775
请不要犹豫，尽管问。
Please don't hesitate to ask.

178
00:10:01,818 --> 00:10:05,363
我们在开拓者感谢你和我们一起度过新年。
We at Trailblazer appreciate you spending your New Year's Day with us.

179
00:10:05,387 --> 00:10:06,954
谢谢你！
Thank you.

180
00:10:06,997 --> 00:10:09,304
你想和他合个影吗?
Hey, do you want to take a picture with him?

181
00:10:09,347 --> 00:10:10,566
——什么?-一张照片。
- What? - A picture.

182
00:10:11,436 --> 00:10:12,437
来吧。
Come on.

183
00:10:17,791 --> 00:10:19,662
-你能不能别这样?——对不起。
- Could you not do that? - Sorry.

184
00:10:28,715 --> 00:10:29,759
美丽的家庭。
Beautiful family.

185
00:10:31,108 --> 00:10:36,070
谢谢你！只是…这是一个杂耍。
Thank you. Just... It's a juggle.

186
00:10:36,113 --> 00:10:37,114
但我们做到了。
But we make it work.

187
00:10:37,854 --> 00:10:39,551
你呢，队长?
How about you, Cap?

188
00:10:39,595 --> 00:10:41,641
-你有家庭吗?-是的，我有一个女儿。
- Do you have a family? - Yeah, I have a daughter.

189
00:10:42,859 --> 00:10:44,861
实际上,在这里。她来了。
Actually, here. Here she is.

190
00:10:47,472 --> 00:10:48,473
丹妮拉。
Daniela.

191
00:10:50,519 --> 00:10:51,607
我看到了相似之处。
I see the resemblance.

192
00:10:51,651 --> 00:10:53,914
你认为呢?
You think?

193
00:10:53,957 --> 00:10:57,221
-家在哪里?-丹妮拉在加州上大学。
- And where's home? - Daniela goes to college in California.

194
00:10:57,265 --> 00:11:02,357
我现在在新加坡工作。
And, uh, I'm based out of Singapore.

195
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:06,013
这么远的距离对你和你妻子来说一定很有挑战性吧?
The distance must be quite challenging for you and your wife, no?

196
00:11:07,362 --> 00:11:10,887
其实我妻子三年前就去世了。
Well, my wife actually passed three years ago.

197
00:11:13,498 --> 00:11:15,805
-我很抱歉，队长-不，不。
- I'm so sorry, Captain. - No, no.

198
00:11:15,849 --> 00:11:18,199
谢谢你！不，没关系。
Thank you. Nah, it's okay.

199
00:11:41,657 --> 00:11:43,615
-新年快乐。-哦，谢谢。
- Happy New Year. - Oh, thank you.

200
00:11:43,659 --> 00:11:44,680
先生，您要点什么?
What can I get for you, sir?

201
00:11:44,704 --> 00:11:45,748
呃,杜松子酒。
Uh, gin.

202
00:11:45,792 --> 00:11:47,619
你要奎宁水或苏打水吗?
Do you need any tonic or soda water?

203
00:11:47,663 --> 00:11:49,099
杜松子酒。只有杜松子酒。
Just gin. Just the gin.

204
00:12:03,070 --> 00:12:05,550
我们正从风暴的顶端穿过。
We're cutting right through the top of the storm.

205
00:12:09,206 --> 00:12:10,642
“搬到内陆”说的也就这么多了。
So much for "moving inland."

206
00:12:12,427 --> 00:12:14,472
女士们先生们，我是机长。
Ladies and gentlemen, this is your captain speaking.

207
00:12:14,516 --> 00:12:16,431
安全带指示灯已经打开。
The seatbelt signs have been turned on.

208
00:12:16,474 --> 00:12:19,216
请留在座位上，系好安全带。谢谢你！
Please remain in your seats with your seatbelts secure. Thank you.

209
00:12:23,481 --> 00:12:27,442
开拓者119号，请求爬升到40000高度以保证天气晴朗。
Trailblazer 119, requesting climb to 40,000 to clear weather.

210
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:36,930
TSN控制中心，这里是开拓者119请求飞行爬升到4万英尺以保证天气良好。拷贝吗?
TSN control, this is Trailblazer 119 requesting flight climb to 40,000 feet to clear weather. Copy?

211
00:12:40,107 --> 00:12:42,065
这里的通讯不太好。
Comms here are not so good.

212
00:12:42,109 --> 00:12:43,545
TCAS没有交通。
TCAS is clear of traffic.

213
00:12:45,634 --> 00:12:48,245
TSN控制中心，这里是开拓者119号。
TSN control, this is Trailblazer 119.

214
00:12:48,289 --> 00:12:51,466
爬升到四万英尺，天气晴朗，在盲区。
Climbing to 40,000 to clear weather, in the blind.

215
00:13:01,389 --> 00:13:03,826
开拓者119号，高度40000。
Trailblazer 119, clear to 40,000.

216
00:13:07,787 --> 00:13:11,007
收到,TSN。开拓者119高度40000。
Copy, TSN. Trailblazer 119 level at 40,000.

217
00:13:13,053 --> 00:13:14,532
新年的船员，嗯?
New Year's crew, huh?

218
00:13:18,972 --> 00:13:20,756
哇。
Whoa.

219
00:13:24,238 --> 00:13:25,326
那是什么?
What was that?

220
00:13:26,980 --> 00:13:28,720
好的。
Okay.

221
00:13:28,764 --> 00:13:30,679
我去检查一下乘客。
I'm gonna check on the passengers.

222
00:13:30,722 --> 00:13:32,507
-你有控制权。-我能控制。
- You have control. - I have control.

223
00:13:36,946 --> 00:13:38,469
伙计们，没什么好担心的。
Nothing to worry about, folks.

224
00:13:38,513 --> 00:13:39,514
只是天气不好。
Just some weather.

225
00:13:41,255 --> 00:13:43,344
-给，邦妮。你没事吧?——哦。是的。
- Here, Bonnie. You okay? - Oh. Yes.

226
00:13:45,781 --> 00:13:48,044
那是什么?
What was that?

227
00:13:48,088 --> 00:13:50,873
对不起,各位。只是在经历一些天气。
Sorry, folks. Just going through some weather.

228
00:13:50,917 --> 00:13:52,657
这是你的吗?
Is this yours?

229
00:13:52,701 --> 00:13:54,790
-那是我的。——哦。给你。
- That's mine. - Oh. Here you go.

230
00:13:54,834 --> 00:13:56,357
谢谢你！
Thank you.

231
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:58,707
他很会讲笑话，但他能开飞机吗?
He's great with the jokes, but can he fly the damn plane?

232
00:13:58,750 --> 00:14:00,970
我们已经尽力了，先生。
We're doing the best we can, sir.

233
00:14:01,014 --> 00:14:02,624
能给我一条毛巾吗?
Hey, can I at least get a towel?

234
00:14:04,104 --> 00:14:05,714
我们会尽快给您安排的。
We'll get you one just as soon as we can.

235
00:14:08,412 --> 00:14:09,718
发生了什么事?你还好吗?
What happened? Are you okay?

236
00:14:09,761 --> 00:14:11,328
哦。所有的好。只是擦伤。
Oh. All good. Just a scratch.

237
00:14:11,372 --> 00:14:12,373
好吧。
All right.

238
00:14:13,548 --> 00:14:14,917
听着，让大家都坐在座位上。
Listen, keep everybody in their seats.

239
00:14:14,941 --> 00:14:16,899
没有例外。好吧?
No exceptions. All right?

240
00:14:35,962 --> 00:14:37,224
把它们系紧。
Strap 'em in tight.

241
00:14:37,267 --> 00:14:38,573
是的,先生。
Yes, sir.

242
00:14:38,616 --> 00:14:40,880
邦妮，坐在你的座位上。
Bonnie, stay in your seat.

243
00:14:40,923 --> 00:14:42,055
发生什么事情了?
What's happening?

244
00:14:43,926 --> 00:14:45,972
机长，航空电子设备坏了。
Captain, avionics are down.

245
00:14:53,805 --> 00:14:55,416
-我能控制。-收到。
- I have control. - Copy that.

246
00:14:56,504 --> 00:14:59,159
检查断路器并复位。——重置。
- Check breakers and reset. - Resetting.

247
00:15:00,377 --> 00:15:03,511
TSN，这里是开拓者119号。听到了吗?
TSN, this is Trailblazer 119. Do you copy?

248
00:15:05,687 --> 00:15:08,603
没有响应。没有电。
Unresponsive. There's no power.

249
00:15:09,647 --> 00:15:12,172
航空电子设备肯定被炸了。大便。
Avionics must be fried. Shit.

250
00:15:13,390 --> 00:15:15,827
有人在这个频道吗?请回应。
Is anyone on this channel? Please respond.

251
00:15:15,871 --> 00:15:18,047
开拓者119号，盲飞。
Trailblazer 119, flying blind.

252
00:15:18,091 --> 00:15:21,964
雷击。航空电子设备。我们是黑暗的。
Lightning strike. Avionics down. We are dark.

253
00:15:22,008 --> 00:15:23,835
有人知道我们的位置吗?
Does anyone have our position?

254
00:15:25,925 --> 00:15:27,796
无线电已经死了。重置。
Radio is dead. Resetting.

255
00:15:32,366 --> 00:15:33,845
系统故障。
System failure.

256
00:15:33,889 --> 00:15:35,021
我们没有信号。
We're not transmitting.

257
00:15:36,413 --> 00:15:37,719
我们正处于电池状态。
We're on straight battery.

258
00:15:39,329 --> 00:15:44,421
在失去动力失控下降之前我们有十分钟时间把她放下。
That gives us 10 minutes to put her down before we lose power and drop into uncontrolled descent.

259
00:15:51,646 --> 00:15:52,864
秒表。
Stopwatch.

260
00:15:52,908 --> 00:15:54,214
什么?
What?

261
00:15:54,257 --> 00:15:55,737
喊出来，德勒。
Call it out, Dele.

262
00:15:55,780 --> 00:15:57,217
一次一分钟，好吗?
One minute at a time, okay?

263
00:15:58,914 --> 00:16:01,134
——好吗?——好的。
- Okay? - Okay.

264
00:16:01,177 --> 00:16:04,920
好的。手动导航。最后标记的位置?
Okay. Manual nav. Last marked position?

265
00:16:09,142 --> 00:16:13,537
427，马尼拉西南偏南，航向0 - 3 - 0。
427, south southwest of Manila, heading zero-three-zero.

266
00:16:14,277 --> 00:16:18,238
考虑到速度和航向，我们应该在这里。
Given speed and heading, we should be about here.

267
00:16:20,980 --> 00:16:22,180
风暴向东北方向移动。
The storm's heading northeast.

268
00:16:23,112 --> 00:16:24,331
我们到不了马尼拉。
We won't make Manila.

269
00:16:27,073 --> 00:16:28,857
求救，求救，求救。
Mayday, Mayday, Mayday.

270
00:16:28,900 --> 00:16:33,340
这里是开拓者119号。从4万英尺下降。
This is Trailblazer 119. Descending from 40,000 feet.

271
00:16:33,383 --> 00:16:37,735
没有雷达，导航，天线，ADI。
No radar, no navigation, no antenna, no ADI.

272
00:16:38,998 --> 00:16:39,999
请回应。
Please respond.

273
00:16:41,826 --> 00:16:43,045
我的天啊。
Oh, my God.

274
00:16:43,089 --> 00:16:44,916
航空电子设备坏了，邦妮。
Avionics are fried, Bonnie.

275
00:16:44,960 --> 00:16:46,266
这将变得非常艰难。
It's about to get very rough.

276
00:16:47,528 --> 00:16:49,182
好的，好的，好的。
Okay, okay, okay.

277
00:16:54,622 --> 00:16:55,927
这是不可能的。
This is not happening.

278
00:16:55,971 --> 00:16:57,320
女士们先生们，我们已经…
Ladies and gentlemen, we've had...

279
00:17:02,456 --> 00:17:09,985
女士们先生们，我们发生了电气故障我需要每个人都系好安全带!
Ladies and gentlemen, we've had an electrical malfunction and I need everyone to have their seatbelts securely fastened!

280
00:17:10,029 --> 00:17:12,466
我们将被迫在恶劣天气中飞行!
We're gonna be forced to fly through some severe weather!

281
00:17:12,509 --> 00:17:14,096
-怎么了?-电气故障!
- What happened? - An electrical malfunction!

282
00:17:14,120 --> 00:17:16,040
我要所有人都系好安全带!
I need everyone's seatbelts to be fully fastened!

283
00:17:21,431 --> 00:17:22,476
队长。
Captain.

284
00:17:29,570 --> 00:17:31,572
——时间?- 8分钟。
- Time? - Eight minutes.

285
00:17:33,139 --> 00:17:36,794
我们要失去月球了。盯着陀螺看。
We're gonna lose the moon. Keep your eyes on the gyro.

286
00:17:36,838 --> 00:17:38,231
大声喊出来。
Call it out.

287
00:17:38,274 --> 00:17:40,274
如果发生什么事，准备好控制局面。
Get ready to take the controls if anything happens.

288
00:17:51,070 --> 00:17:52,071
这就是冰雹。
That's hail.

289
00:17:53,159 --> 00:17:54,290
现在是派对了。
Now it's a party.

290
00:17:55,422 --> 00:17:59,600
大便。我们必须冲破这场风暴，看看我们能到哪里去。
Shit. We gotta punch through this storm and see where we come out.

291
00:18:14,702 --> 00:18:18,009
我的电话。
My phone.

292
00:18:18,053 --> 00:18:20,055
-通不过去。-我也不是。
- It's not going through. - Neither is mine.

293
00:18:21,448 --> 00:18:24,625
来吧，宝贝。抓住。抓住。
Come on, baby. Hold tight. Hold tight.

294
00:18:24,668 --> 00:18:26,453
我的天啊。的帮助!
Oh, my God. Help!

295
00:18:27,628 --> 00:18:30,370
你能把手铐解开吗?我不会游泳。
Can you take off the cuffs? I can't swim.

296
00:18:32,241 --> 00:18:33,329
不可能。
Not a chance.

297
00:18:40,684 --> 00:18:43,165
去吧，去吧。我抓住你了。我抓住你了。
Go ahead, go ahead. I got you. I got you.

298
00:18:43,209 --> 00:18:45,254
该死的飞机要散架了!
The goddamn plane is falling apart!

299
00:18:51,521 --> 00:18:52,566
狗屎!
Shit!

300
00:18:56,744 --> 00:18:59,138
-先生，请坐。——先生?先生?坐下来。
- Sir, you must take your seat. - Sir? Sir? Sit down.

301
00:19:01,052 --> 00:19:02,837
待在这里。待在这儿，伊莎贝拉。只留下。
Stay here. Stay here, Isabella. Just stay.

302
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:04,075
-坐着别动。-坐下!
- Just stay seated. - Sit down!

303
00:19:04,099 --> 00:19:05,405
-坐下!-坐下!
- Sit down! - Sit down!

304
00:19:08,799 --> 00:19:10,149
伊莎贝拉!
Isabella!

305
00:19:12,063 --> 00:19:13,413
哦，天哪!
Oh, my God!

306
00:19:15,023 --> 00:19:16,067
哇。
Whoa.

307
00:19:16,111 --> 00:19:18,157
你能帮帮她吗?
Could you help her?

308
00:19:19,723 --> 00:19:21,029
时间吗?
Time?

309
00:19:21,072 --> 00:19:22,312
五分四十秒。
Five minutes and forty seconds.

310
00:19:27,949 --> 00:19:30,169
来吧。来吧，突破。
Come on. Come on, break through.

311
00:19:32,780 --> 00:19:34,260
哦,他妈的。
Oh, fuck.

312
00:19:53,279 --> 00:19:54,454
好了。
There you go.

313
00:19:59,633 --> 00:20:00,764
时间吗?
Time?

314
00:20:00,808 --> 00:20:02,244
4分30秒。
Four minutes and thirty seconds.

315
00:20:02,853 --> 00:20:03,854
好的。
Okay.

316
00:20:04,725 --> 00:20:06,117
你能看到陆地吗?
Can you see land anywhere?

317
00:20:14,822 --> 00:20:16,215
先生，请坐。
Please, sir, sit down.

318
00:20:17,825 --> 00:20:19,783
请大家留在座位上。
Everyone stay in their seats, please.

319
00:20:32,318 --> 00:20:35,277
机长，我该怎么跟乘客说?
Captain, what do I tell the passengers?

320
00:20:41,109 --> 00:20:43,067
从没想过我会说这些。
Never thought I would ever have to say this.

321
00:20:49,160 --> 00:20:50,205
准备迫降。
Prepare to ditch.

322
00:20:54,427 --> 00:20:55,471
好的。
Okay.

323
00:21:00,563 --> 00:21:02,435
大家注意!
Attention, everyone!

324
00:21:02,478 --> 00:21:05,133
我要你准备好迎接撞击!
I need you to brace for impact!

325
00:21:05,176 --> 00:21:07,614
飞机上装有漂浮装置。
The plane is equipped with flotation devices.

326
00:21:07,657 --> 00:21:11,574
-我们要坠毁了-一旦我们下来，我会给你进一步的指示!
- We're gonna crash. - And once we are down, I will give you further instruction!

327
00:21:11,618 --> 00:21:13,073
-玛丽亚，你听到了吗?-我们在哪里降落?
- Maria, do you hear me? - Where are we landing?

328
00:21:13,097 --> 00:21:15,796
是的，收到!准备好撞击!
Yes, copy that! Brace for impact!

329
00:21:19,887 --> 00:21:21,845
那些白色的帽子看起来不太受欢迎。
Those white caps don't look too welcoming.

330
00:21:25,153 --> 00:21:26,154
时间吗?
Time?

331
00:21:28,025 --> 00:21:29,113
三分钟。
Three minutes.

332
00:21:53,616 --> 00:21:57,272
好了，黛勒。让我们全力以赴吧。
All right, Dele. Let's give this our best shot.

333
00:21:58,926 --> 00:22:06,325
听我的命令，我们要转向迎风，我们要与海浪平行，所以我们要缓慢而水平地降落。
On my command, we're gonna turn into the wind and we're gonna come in parallel to the swells, so we touch down slow and level.

334
00:22:07,804 --> 00:22:09,284
