1004
01:23:26,697 --> 01:23:27,897
我不知道发生了什么。
I don't know what's happening.

1005
01:23:29,830 --> 01:23:30,962
或者你受伤了。
Or if you're hurt.

1006
01:23:33,356 --> 01:23:34,444
我好害怕。
I'm so scared.

1007
01:23:36,663 --> 01:23:38,013
所以，请回家吧。
So, just please come home.

1008
01:23:48,980 --> 01:23:51,026
开拓者CP，这里是Shellback 6号。
Trailblazer CP, this is Shellback 6.

1009
01:23:51,069 --> 01:23:53,811
等一下，收到，6。你现在怎么样?
Let's wait a sec. Copy, 6. What's your status?

1010
01:23:53,854 --> 01:23:56,422
人质安全，但我们有另一个计划。
Hostages secure, but we've got another plan.

1011
01:23:56,466 --> 01:23:57,728
你不会喜欢的。
You're not gonna like it.

1012
01:23:57,771 --> 01:23:58,859
来吧。每个人,快点。
Come on. Everybody, hurry.

1013
01:23:58,903 --> 01:24:00,165
快跑，快跑，快跑!
Run, run, run!

1014
01:24:00,209 --> 01:24:01,558
嘿，把他们聚集在这里。
Hey, gather them here.

1015
01:24:01,601 --> 01:24:03,342
-大家，来吧。-围过来。
- Everyone, come on. - Gather around.

1016
01:24:03,386 --> 01:24:05,214
来吧!
Come on!

1017
01:24:05,257 --> 01:24:11,481
现在，在未来24小时内，不会有完整的救援队伍很快到来。
Now, there is no full rescue team coming anytime soon, not for the next 24 hours.

1018
01:24:11,524 --> 01:24:13,091
——什么?-我们等不及了。
- What? - We can't wait.

1019
01:24:13,135 --> 01:24:17,922
他们会使出浑身解数来对付我们，我们会死的。
They are gonna come at us with everything they've got, and we're not gonna survive.

1020
01:24:17,965 --> 01:24:21,621
我和德勒设法恢复了飞机上的电力。
Now, Dele and I managed to get the power back up on the plane.

1021
01:24:21,665 --> 01:24:22,883
来自西区。
From the west end.

1022
01:24:22,927 --> 01:24:25,103
我们只有一次机会。
We only have one chance.

1023
01:24:25,147 --> 01:24:27,627
那就是我开着这玩意飞出去。
And that is me flying us out of here in this thing.

1024
01:24:27,671 --> 01:24:28,822
-等等，等等。什么?-不可能。
- Wait, wait, wait. What? - No way in hell.

1025
01:24:28,846 --> 01:24:30,978
-我知道。-听着，听着。
- I know. - Listen, listen.

1026
01:24:31,022 --> 01:24:33,285
听，听，听!
Listen, listen, listen!

1027
01:24:33,329 --> 01:24:37,420
如果我不相信能成功，我就不会把你们放回飞机上。
If I didn't believe it could be done, I would not put you guys back on that plane.

1028
01:24:39,161 --> 01:24:40,814
我有一个女儿。
I have a daughter.

1029
01:24:40,858 --> 01:24:44,905
我很想再次拥抱她，然后回家。
I have every intention of hugging her again and making it home.

1030
01:24:44,949 --> 01:24:48,083
我告诉你，回家的路就在这架飞机上。
And I'm telling you that the way home is on this plane.

1031
01:24:49,171 --> 01:24:50,563
我已经带你到这里了。
I've got you this far.

1032
01:24:50,607 --> 01:24:53,566
我只需要你再相信我一点。好吗?
I just need you to trust me this one more bit. Okay?

1033
01:24:53,610 --> 01:24:55,283
-好的，飞行前检查。-收到。
- All right, preflight checks. - Copy that.

1034
01:24:55,307 --> 01:24:56,893
-大家跟着德勒先生。-跟我来。
- Everybody, follow Mr. Dele. - Follow me, come on.

1035
01:24:56,917 --> 01:24:58,789
——好的。好吧。-来吧!
- Okay. All right. - Come on!

1036
01:25:01,574 --> 01:25:02,836
来吧!
Come on!

1037
01:25:02,880 --> 01:25:04,360
Shellback，我还能活多久?
Shellback, how long have I got?

1038
01:25:04,403 --> 01:25:05,535
最多两分钟。
Two minutes tops.

1039
01:25:05,578 --> 01:25:10,279
不能确定已经造成的损坏不会影响飞行特性，也不能确定引擎不会失灵。
Can't be certain the damage already done won't affect flight characteristics or that the engines won't fail.

1040
01:25:10,322 --> 01:25:11,584
Shellback说可以做到。
Shellback said it can be done.

1041
01:25:11,628 --> 01:25:12,759
他是地面上的人。
He's the man on the ground.

1042
01:25:12,803 --> 01:25:15,260
由于缺乏适当的检查，他没有资格作出那项决定。
Short of proper inspection, he's not qualified to make that determination.

1043
01:25:15,284 --> 01:25:16,850
他们被追捕了，特里。
They're being hunted, Terry.

1044
01:25:16,894 --> 01:25:18,417
你说的是检查?
And you're talking about inspections?

1045
01:25:18,461 --> 01:25:24,031
在他们经历了这么多之后，想象一下如果我允许托伦斯驾驶那架飞机并烧死飞机上的所有人会有什么后果。
After all they've been through, imagine the fallout if I allow Torrance to fly that plane and incinerate everybody in it.

1046
01:25:24,075 --> 01:25:25,685
想象一下如果你不这样做的后果。
Imagine the fallout if you don't.

1047
01:25:25,729 --> 01:25:27,098
确保他们顺利上车。来吧。
Make sure they get on okay. Come on.

1048
01:25:27,122 --> 01:25:28,862
快跑，快跑，快跑!
Run, run, run!

1049
01:25:33,693 --> 01:25:34,781
每个人都在。
Everybody on.

1050
01:25:38,176 --> 01:25:39,536
来吧。我们走吧。我们走吧，玛丽亚。
Come on. Let's go. Let's go, Maria.

1051
01:25:44,400 --> 01:25:45,531
啊,操。
Ah, fuck.

1052
01:25:46,967 --> 01:25:48,380
马上就会有一堆坏人找我们麻烦了。
We're about to have a lot of bad guys up our asses.

1053
01:25:48,404 --> 01:25:49,903
我需要你加快速度，队长。
I'm gonna need you to pick up the pace, Cap.

1054
01:25:49,927 --> 01:25:54,410
-好吧。-我们在这里和这里有两个车队，看起来第三个车队也不远了。
- All right. - We've got two convoys here and here, and it looks like a third is not far behind.

1055
01:25:54,453 --> 01:25:55,778
好吧。我得先把刹车修好。
All right. I gotta fix this brake first.

1056
01:25:55,802 --> 01:25:57,978
-你得给我争取点时间-知道了。
- You gotta buy me some time. - Got it.

1057
01:26:04,028 --> 01:26:05,464
就像她说的，走吧。我们走吧。
Like she said, let's go. Let's go.

1058
01:26:16,693 --> 01:26:17,955
——移动!——邦妮!
- Move! - Bonnie!

1059
01:26:17,998 --> 01:26:19,435
我知道了，上尉!的帮助!
I got it, Captain! Help!

1060
01:26:20,523 --> 01:26:21,654
继续前进。
Keep moving.

1061
01:26:28,095 --> 01:26:29,488
动!我找不到他。
Move! I can't get him.

1062
01:26:30,837 --> 01:26:31,882
快，快，快!
Move, move, move!

1063
01:26:33,013 --> 01:26:35,102
该走了，上尉!该走了!
Time to go, Captain! Time to go now!

1064
01:27:00,127 --> 01:27:01,172
重新加载!
Reloading!

1065
01:27:12,792 --> 01:27:13,793
移动!
Moving!

1066
01:27:53,268 --> 01:27:55,226
老水手!Shellback，我需要通讯。
Shellback! Shellback, I need comms.

1067
01:27:56,401 --> 01:27:57,681
已经在团队频道播出了。
It's already on the team channel.

1068
01:27:59,099 --> 01:28:01,232
一旦我启动引擎，你有两分钟时间。
Once I start the engines, you have two minutes.

1069
01:28:01,276 --> 01:28:03,321
-我不走楼梯了。-收到。
- I'll leave the stairs down. - Roger that.

1070
01:28:05,323 --> 01:28:07,107
你知道我不能和你一起上飞机。
You know I can't get on that plane with you.

1071
01:28:07,151 --> 01:28:10,807
——对吗?-好吧。祝你好运。
- Right? - Yeah, okay. Good luck.

1072
01:28:12,287 --> 01:28:13,853
你也是，我的船长。
You too, my capitan.

1073
01:28:46,886 --> 01:28:49,236
想办法把他绑起来，邦妮。
Find a way to strap him in, Bonnie.

1074
01:28:49,280 --> 01:28:50,934
大家都趴下，好吗?
Everybody, stay down, okay?

1075
01:28:50,977 --> 01:28:52,979
再陪我一段时间。
Just hang with me just a little bit longer.

1076
01:28:53,023 --> 01:28:55,025
如果不重启舱门就封不上。
The cabin doors won't seal without a reset.

1077
01:28:55,068 --> 01:28:57,810
所有的门都打开，好吗?所以它们是平衡的。
Keep them open, all of them, okay? So they're balanced.

1078
01:28:59,638 --> 01:29:02,685
航空电子设备仍然故障。屏幕上什么都没有。
Avionics still shot. Nothing on screens.

1079
01:29:02,728 --> 01:29:04,948
检查了液压系统。它们看起来不错。
Checked the hydraulics. They look good.

1080
01:29:04,991 --> 01:29:06,384
好的。APU工作吗?
Okay. APU working?

1081
01:29:06,428 --> 01:29:08,081
- APU工作正常。——订婚?
- APU working. - Engaged?

1082
01:29:08,125 --> 01:29:09,909
——参与。——好的。
- Engaged. - Okay.

1083
01:29:09,953 --> 01:29:10,954
好了，黛勒。
All right, Dele.

1084
01:29:12,999 --> 01:29:14,261
启动它们。
Start 'em up.

1085
01:29:14,305 --> 01:29:16,002
起动发动机。
Starting engines.

1086
01:29:19,266 --> 01:29:21,834
-你还好吗?-是的，我没事。
- You okay? - Yeah, I'm okay.

1087
01:29:21,878 --> 01:29:23,183
下来!
Get down!

1088
01:29:32,584 --> 01:29:34,412
大便。我没子弹了。
Shit. I'm out of ammo.

1089
01:29:34,456 --> 01:29:36,458
检查我们的托盘。湖,重新加载!
Check our pallet. Lake, reloading!

1090
01:29:51,255 --> 01:29:52,343
重新加载!
Reloading!

1091
01:30:09,012 --> 01:30:10,143
大便。
Shit.

1092
01:30:16,498 --> 01:30:17,673
我需要你和我在一起，黛勒。
I need you with me, Dele.

1093
01:30:17,716 --> 01:30:18,761
集中注意力。
Keep your focus in here.

1094
01:30:19,501 --> 01:30:20,763
嘿，进入直播。
Hey, into the live.

1095
01:30:21,807 --> 01:30:23,026
让我们把它转过来。
Let's turn this baby around.

1096
01:30:37,432 --> 01:30:38,998
他们击中了我们的油箱，我们就完了。
They hit our fuel tanks, we're toast.

1097
01:30:49,879 --> 01:30:51,141
我是托伦斯上尉。
This is Captain Torrance.

1098
01:30:51,184 --> 01:30:53,360
有人在吗?
Is anyone there?

1099
01:30:53,404 --> 01:30:55,754
有人在吗，该死的?我要走了。
Is anyone there, God damn it? I'm about to take off.

1100
01:30:55,798 --> 01:30:58,496
上尉，你听我说。那架飞机就在她所在的地方。
Captain, you listen to me. That plane stays right where she is.

1101
01:30:58,540 --> 01:31:02,369
-明白了吗?-托伦斯上尉，我叫大卫·斯卡斯代尔。告诉我你需要什么。
- Am I understood? - Captain Torrance, my name is David Scarsdale. Tell me what you need.

1102
01:31:02,413 --> 01:31:04,241
我需要方向性的帮助。
I need directional assistance.

1103
01:31:04,284 --> 01:31:07,157
我们没有雷达，也没有导航。我们完全是手工操作。
We have no radar, no nav. We are fully manual.

1104
01:31:07,200 --> 01:31:09,725
我想我们最多还有300英里。
I figure we've got about 300 miles tops.

1105
01:31:09,768 --> 01:31:11,291
给我找个地方降落。
Find me a place to land.

1106
01:31:13,685 --> 01:31:15,034
老水手。
Shellback.

1107
01:31:15,078 --> 01:31:17,210
我要你和你的人马上上飞机。
I need you and your men on the plane now.

1108
01:31:17,254 --> 01:31:19,517
我们一转弯我就走。
I'm gonna go as soon as we make this turn.

1109
01:31:19,561 --> 01:31:20,910
-快上飞机!——检查。
- Get to the plane! - Check.

1110
01:31:22,128 --> 01:31:23,129
掩护我!
Cover me!

1111
01:31:29,222 --> 01:31:30,572
我们走吧!
Let's go!

1112
01:31:39,624 --> 01:31:41,234
我们有足够的路吗?
Do we have enough road?

1113
01:31:41,278 --> 01:31:42,322
必须如此。
It's gonna have to be.

1114
01:31:43,106 --> 01:31:44,760
Gaspare,移动!动!
Gaspare, move! Move!

1115
01:31:47,763 --> 01:31:48,807
Gaspare,移动!
Gaspare, move!

1116
01:31:53,595 --> 01:31:54,726
Gaspare !
Gaspare!

1117
01:31:54,770 --> 01:31:55,814
来吧!
Come on!

1118
01:32:01,646 --> 01:32:02,865
我们走吧!
Let's go!

1119
01:32:03,605 --> 01:32:05,258
我的翅膀清晰。
My wing clear.

1120
01:32:05,302 --> 01:32:06,564
我的翅膀是干净的。
My wing is clear.

1121
01:32:10,742 --> 01:32:12,178
不能再等了，Shellback。
Can't wait any longer, Shellback.

1122
01:32:12,222 --> 01:32:13,223
你现在怎么样?
What's your status?

1123
01:32:14,746 --> 01:32:16,443
继续。带我们上去，船长。
Go on. Take us up, Captain.

1124
01:32:31,284 --> 01:32:32,547
下来!
Get down!

1125
01:32:51,914 --> 01:32:53,089
搞什么鬼?
What the fuck?

1126
01:33:25,469 --> 01:33:26,470
全油门。
Full throttle.

1127
01:34:08,381 --> 01:34:10,296
队长，你的肩膀。
Cap, your shoulder.

1128
01:34:10,340 --> 01:34:11,820
我很好。
I'm okay.

1129
01:34:16,041 --> 01:34:17,782
我们失去动力了，右引擎。
We're losing power, right engine.

1130
01:34:17,826 --> 01:34:19,218
-关闭。——不!
- Shutting it down. - No!

1131
01:34:19,262 --> 01:34:21,699
我们需要所有的推力。
We need all the thrust we can get.

1132
01:34:21,743 --> 01:34:24,876
-我们要撞上了。我们要撞上了。-保存左引擎。
- We're gonna hit. We're gonna hit. - Save left engine.

1133
01:34:27,749 --> 01:34:28,750
来吧。
Come on.

1134
01:34:37,889 --> 01:34:40,413
右引擎失灵。现在就把它关掉。
Lost right engine. Shut it down now.

1135
01:34:40,457 --> 01:34:41,545
关闭两个。
Shutting down two.

1136
01:34:48,639 --> 01:34:50,162
有多糟糕?
How bad?

1137
01:34:50,206 --> 01:34:52,382
右翼后缘受损。
Right wing's trailing edge is damaged.

1138
01:34:52,425 --> 01:34:54,689
大便。好吧，盯着点。
Shit. Okay, just keep an eye on it.

1139
01:34:55,777 --> 01:34:57,343
这里是开拓者119号。
This is Trailblazer 119.

1140
01:34:58,431 --> 01:34:59,911
我们空降。
We're airborne.

1141
01:34:59,955 --> 01:35:03,654
开拓者119号，收到你的航速135节。
Trailblazer 119, reading your air speed at 135 knots.

1142
01:35:04,394 --> 01:35:05,612
边界失速率。
Bordering stall rate.

1143
01:35:05,656 --> 01:35:07,310
这是她最快的速度了。
This is as fast as she'll go.

1144
01:35:07,353 --> 01:35:09,312
高度400英尺。
Reading your altitude at 400 feet.

1145
01:35:09,355 --> 01:35:12,097
你得让她升到3000，不然她就睡不着了。
You need to take her up to 3,000 or she's not staying up.

1146
01:35:12,141 --> 01:35:14,230
没有速度和高度。
Negative on speed and altitude.

1147
01:35:14,273 --> 01:35:16,536
119号，你得马上带她上去。
119, you need to take her up now.

1148
01:35:16,580 --> 01:35:18,582
我们没有该死的门。
We have no fucking doors.

1149
01:35:18,625 --> 01:35:23,892
我们降压了，燃料不足了，我们刚刚失去了一个引擎。别跟我说我已经知道的事。
We're depressurized, we're low on fuel and we just lost an engine. Now, don't tell me what I already know.

1150
01:35:23,935 --> 01:35:25,415
给我找个地方降落。
Find me a place to land.

1151
01:35:28,940 --> 01:35:30,855
正在调出可用机场的名单。
Pulling up lists of available airfields now.

1152
01:35:30,899 --> 01:35:32,683
让我们把它放到屏幕上。
Let's get it up on the screen.

1153
01:35:32,727 --> 01:35:36,426
最好的选择，西亚岛，正南50英里。
Best option, Siasi Island, 50 miles due south.

1154
01:35:36,469 --> 01:35:39,298
调整你的航向到15度。那里有一个小机场。
Adjust your heading to 15 degrees. There's a small airport there.

1155
01:35:39,342 --> 01:35:40,735
你能来吗?
Can you make it?

1156
01:35:40,778 --> 01:35:42,606
我们会找到答案的。
We're gonna find out.

1157
01:35:43,694 --> 01:35:45,914
丛林中清除。脚湿了。
Jungle cleared. Feet wet.

1158
01:35:49,656 --> 01:35:51,658
看到西亚西了。
Have a visual on Siasi.

1159
01:35:51,702 --> 01:35:54,096
来吧。来吧，宝贝。再多一点。
Come on. Come on, baby. Just a little bit more.

1160
01:35:55,010 --> 01:35:56,620
失去右侧控制。
Lost right-side control.

1161
01:36:01,712 --> 01:36:02,713
失去高度。
Losing altitude.

1162
01:36:09,807 --> 01:36:11,374
可以看到西亚跑道。
Have a visual on Siasi runway.

1163
01:36:13,419 --> 01:36:15,465
准备降落!
Prepare for landing!

1164
01:36:15,508 --> 01:36:17,423
准备好撞击!准备好撞击!
Brace for impact! Brace for impact!

1165
01:36:30,436 --> 01:36:31,611
完全倒车。
Full reverse on one.

1166
01:36:32,787 --> 01:36:33,962
速度刹车。
Speed brakes.

1167
01:36:37,356 --> 01:36:38,749
帮我踩刹车，德勒。
Help me on the brakes, Dele.

1168
01:36:52,937 --> 01:36:54,025
哦。
Oh.

1169
01:37:03,295 --> 01:37:04,731
我们没事吧?
Are we okay?

1170
01:37:04,775 --> 01:37:05,907
是的。
Yes.

1171
01:37:17,919 --> 01:37:19,094
好工作。
Good job.

1172
01:37:19,137 --> 01:37:21,357
祝贺你,每一个人。谢谢你！
Congratulations, everyone. Thank you.

1173
01:37:25,535 --> 01:37:26,753
你没事吧?
You okay?

1174
01:37:29,931 --> 01:37:31,019
我有过更好的日子。
I've had better days.

1175
01:37:33,935 --> 01:37:35,055
一次一分钟，对吧?
One minute at a time, right?

1176
01:37:36,546 --> 01:37:37,634
一次一分钟。
